  "title": "Healthcare Assistant*(5430)",
  "description": "<h4><strong>Job Purpose</strong></h4>\n<p>The job-holder is responsible to provide personalised, specialised and cost-effective care to the patients in accordance to established</p>\n<p><strong>Duties &amp; Responsibilities and Duties (80%)</strong></p>\n<p>· Assists in providing basic care for patients and general duties</p>\n<p>· Assists in observing and reporting patient’s condition and progress</p>\n<p>· Assists nurses in carrying out procedures</p>\n<p>· Observes, collects and tests specimens as instructed</p>\n<p>· Assists with admission and orientation of conscious patients with stable condition</p>\n<p>· Maintains clean and safe environment</p>\n<p>· Assists with general duties as assigned by Nurse Manager/Senior Nurse Manager</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Completed HCA course</p>\n<p>· Able to commit to 3 rotating shifts</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
